OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally cloudy and mostly dry
OL,6,Fthrough Tuesday morning. Slow-moving
OL,7,Fshowers look set to arrive and turn
OL,8,Fheavy with thunder, especially later
OL,9,Fin the afternoon and into the evening.
OL,10,FTurning dry overnight with winds
OL,11,Fcontinuing light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading during Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening then a fine night with some
OL,15,Fcloud breaks, allowing temperatures to
OL,16,Fdip. Winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
